etwork. Finally, comparing these two new measures\nof persistence and dominance between different countries allows us to classify\nthese countries based the their embeddedness, measured using the relation\nbetween the centrality of a country's firms on the national and the global\nscale of the board interlock network.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 26 May 2016 09:03:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-03-27"}
